# FILE: halabLibrary/halabLibrary.desc
# ROLE: High-Performance Digital Archive & Research Hub
# ROUTE: /library
# ACCOUNT: All account types can browse — download open to all
# THEME: Dark · technical repository · amber badges for university-native

## DESIGN SYSTEM
- PAGE BG: bg-[#070C18] + subtle teal glow top-center
- SECTION HEADERS: section-label pill + gradient-text h2
- GRID CARDS: bg-[#0F1828] · border border-[#1E2D45] · rounded-2xl

## 1. KNOWLEDGE SIDEBAR (Primary Navigation)
- STYLE: sticky · bg-[#0F1828] · border border-[#1E2D45] · rounded-2xl
- BRANCH LIST: vertical, scrollable
  - Active branch: bg-[#6366F1]/15 · border-l-2 border-[#6366F1] · text-[#818CF8]
  - Others: text-[#94A3B8] · hover:text-[#F1F5F9]
- BRANCHES: Admin-controlled — mirrors Academy branch categories

## 2. MULTI-FILTER HUD (Search + Type)
- SEARCH INPUT: real-time fuzzy · bg-[#0F1828] · border-[#1E2D45] · focus:border-[#6366F1]
- TYPE TABS: 📚 كتب كاملة · 📝 ملخصات · 🎓 نماذج امتحانات
- SORT: حجم الملف · تاريخ الإضافة · التقييم

## 3. KNOWLEDGE GRID
- CARD COMPONENTS:
  - FORMAT BADGE: "PDF" or "MD" — muted pill
  - UNIVERSITY BADGE: "🏛️ جامعة حلب" — amber/gold border card variant
  - STUDENT-AUTHORED BADGE: "✍️ طالب" — teal badge (for Shorts category)
  - TITLE, AUTHOR, YEAR
  - SIZE + PAGE COUNT: text-[#4A5D78] text-sm monospace
  - DOWNLOAD BUTTON: ghost or gradient-bg depending on access
- ACTION: click → /library/viewer/:docId

## 4. XP AWARD ON DOWNLOAD (Students)
- When a student downloads a resource: +25 XP awarded
- Toast notification: "حصلت على +25 XP 🎉"

## 5. ADMIN SYNC
- Content, file links, and student-authored "Shorts" verification managed via /admin/library
